if youngDrivers
    .container.py-3
        .row
            .col
                p.h2.text-uppercase Car insurance for young drivers in #{stateTitle}
                p.lead
                    | Young drivers across the U.S. pay more than others. Lack of driving experience entails various risks, that is why the cost of car insurance for such customers is about three times bigger than the national average and sometimes more.
                table.table.table-sm.table-hover.table-borderless.table-striped
                    thead
                        tr
                            th.w-50 Age
                            th(scope='col') Avg. Monthly Premium
                    tbody
                            tr
                                td 16
                                td #{youngDrivers.age16} $
                            tr
                                td 17
                                td #{youngDrivers.age17} $
                            tr
                                td 18
                                td #{youngDrivers.age18} $
                            tr
                                td 19
                                td #{youngDrivers.age19} $
                p.h3.text-uppercase Insurance rate decreases depending on age of driver
